{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider\/spaces"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaces"},{"kind":"text","text":": any "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B38ThemeBulletListComponentTokensProviderC6spaces0A8Contract016AllSpaceSemanticgH0_pvp","title":"spaces","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaces"},{"kind":"text","text":": any "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for link spaces"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSBulletList","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllBulletListComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"BulletListComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider